summary: An ordinance providing for the purchase of the west 30 feet of Tract No. 27, of Sarah B. Yesler's Donation Claim, the same being a part of Temple Place produced from the north line of said tract No. 27, west to the intersection of Temple Place produced to the north line of Yesler Way; authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller of the City of Seattle, to draw a warrant in favor of May H. Wilson, and J. P. Wilson, her husband, for the said property and making an appropriation therefor.
